<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.9">
<l>vēlkoḷ kaittalat taracarvem pōriṉil vicayaṉuk kāymaṇittērk</l>
<l>kōlkoḷ kaittalat tentaipem māṉiṭam kulavutaṇ varaiccāral</l>
<l>kālkoḷ kaṇkoṭik kaiyeḻak kamukiḷam pāḷaikaḷ kamaḻcāral</l>
<l>cēlkaḷ pāytaru ceḻunati vayalpuku tiruvayin tirapuramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the great lord, our father in the palm of whose hand</l>
<l rend="indent">was a horsewhip [for a] jeweled chariot</l>
<l>For the sake of Vijaya in the fierce war with kings</l>
<l rend="indent">in the palm of whose hands were spears, </l>
<l>Is Tiruvayintirapuram where the swollen river flows into fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where carp jump aimlessly in the drizzling wind</l>
<l rend="indent">scented by tender bracts of the areca [palm],</l>
<l>As the [betel] vines wave their [leaf] hands over [the palm’s joint] eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">on its leg[-like trunk] on the cool, rounded slopes of the hill.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
